'09/10/2017 Patron de difraccion simulado 
 
'residuos to see goodness of the fit 
r_wp  15.304083
 
'write standad deviations 
do_errors 
 
'The maximum number of refinement iterations, iters is set to 500000 by default 
iters 1000 
 
'chi2_convergence_criteria value of 0.001 is sufficient for routine refinements 
chi2_convergence_criteria 0.0001 
 
Difractometro() 
  
'Reading the diffraction pattern 
xdd Fluoresceina_interpolated.xy 'DOI:10.1002/anie.199707701
 
'Next line is necessary if the diffraction pattern is a xy-file 
'x_calculation_step 0205018 
'Modeling backgrond	 
  bkg @  193.9618`_13.6220584  208.816698`_17.0089507 -244.886655`_9.7949721  185.425685`_6.63977978
  	One_on_X(@, 4255.56005`_198.4004) 
 
'Specimen is outside of diffraction plane	 
   Specimen_Displacement(@,-0.366644833`_0.00107500822) 
 
'Definition of the crystal structure 
str 
  phase_name  "Fluorosceina" 
    scale @  0.000557348829`_1.775e-06
 
'unit cell 
  space_group "Pn2_1a" 
  a 10.470786_0.001047 '10.4595
  b 13.172828_0.001023 '13.219
  c 10.556286_0.000926 '10.5664
  al  90.00000  
  be=Get(al);
  ga=Get(al);
 
