  site O1  x 0.976 y 0.364 z 0.298 occ O 1.0 
  site O2  x 0.613 y 0.148 z 0.303 occ O 1.0 
  site O3  x 0.277 y -0.082 z 0.333 occ O 1.0 
  site O4  x 0.385 y 0.309 z -0.235 occ O 1.0 
  site O5  x 0.453 y 0.290 z -0.039 occ O 1.0 

  prm avrg_size_fluorescein  91.7876657`_1.32828592
  lor_fwhm = 5.72957 Lam / (Cos(Th) avrg_size_fluorescein) ;  
  
  spherical_harmonics_hkl sh_po
    sh_order 10 load sh_Cij_prm {
      y00  sh_po_c00  1.02114`_0.00309
      y20  sh_po_c20  0.08918`_0.01170
      y22p sh_po_c22p -0.07057`_0.01550
